CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 9, 1967, pg. 15, reads: "ULG Boat Ride - For the past few years, one of the social highlights of the season has been a boat ride sponsored by the Urban League Guild of Pittsburgh. This year was no exception and a happy throng was on hand for the event held recently...Enjoying a chat together on-deck are Shirley Lavine, Judy Davenport, Jim Lavine and Vivian Allen...- All Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Shirley Lavine, Judy Davenport, Jim Lavine, and Vivian Allen standing on deck of riverboat for Urban League Guild of Pittsburgh's annual boat ride, with bridge in background
